Breakfast is an imperative meal of the day that you should not miss at all. Experts suggest to have a heavy breakfast since it helps to boost the energy of anyone all the day long. Today the beautiful princess Elsa is going to prepare the delicious breakfast in her restaurant to satisfy the food urges of her clients. You as a player in this free online cooking game for girls have to help the princess to prepare and serve the tasty breakfast dish properly. 

Elsa is a big lover of breakfast and, for this reason, she has recently made an inauguration of a new restaurant to serve this purpose. Today she is going to prepare an unpopular breakfast â€“ hot dogs. Hope you will help the lady to get the job done perfectly in this brand new online cooking game for girls and boys. Initially, you will have to create the recipe of hot dogs, ice cream cones and coffee then serve it properly to her customers. 

Boil the sausage and then opt for putting it in a bun to cook hot dogs. Add the toppings to it if customers ask for it. Make sure that your order is created before the customers walk in. If they leave the restaurant with an unhappy attitude, you would not be able to earn the bonus points that would help to win this cool html5 game. Get fresh and tasty croissants with butter, new toppings for the most delicious hot dogs and other stations to act upon. The more money you will get, the easier it will be for you to reach the advanced level.
